title: January Brainstorm
author: VD
content_html: I’m sorry about the short notice, but if you’re in technology, this is a Brainstorm you do NOT want to miss if you are a member. Friday, 5:30 PM EST. Closed session, no transcript. We’ll be discussing the new projects that are underway, including the Big Enchilada, with a panelist who is working on an equally important project that every reader here will want to support. Invites go out shortly.
